name: Help Me, I'm Single with Blaine Anderson

episodes.title: Cult Recruitment Date w/ Allison Wojtowecz
episodes.description: Has your date ever tried to recruit you to their cult?? Blaine is joined by the insightful and funny Allison Wojtowecz to audit the dating life of JENSON! The team brainstorms why he keeps getting ghosted and Jenson shares a bizarre story of trying to return his date's driver's license! Allison also shares a terrible Hinge date story and how the pandemic has affected her dating life! PLUS: Is it okay to ask if you can kiss someone? Is it possible to flirt with an entire group of women? Can spending more time at the grocery store help your love life? AND Jenson's Dating Profile Audit!
